---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Evoluția Costurilor PPC (2024-2026): Analiză Comparativă și Tabel de Date";
const description = "Analiză detaliată a costurilor CPC pe Google, Meta și TikTok cu predicții pentru 2026.";
---

<Layout title={title}>
	<main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 max-w-4xl">
		<article class="prose prose-invert lg:prose-xl text-slate-300">
			<span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm italic">Data & Analiză 2026</span>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-black mt-4 mb-8 leading-tight text-white">{title}</h1>
			
			<img src="/assets/ppc-trends.png" alt="PPC Trends 2026" class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 mb-12 shadow-2xl" />

			<p class="text-xl mb-12">{description}</p>

			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Analiză Cantitativă</h2>
			
			<div class="overflow-x-auto my-10">
				<table class="min-w-full bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 rounded-xl">
					<thead>
						<tr>
							<th class="px-6 py-4 text-left border-b border-white/10">An</th>
							<th class="px-6 py-4 text-left border-b border-white/10">Platforma</th>
							<th class="px-6 py-4 text-left border-b border-white/10">Metrica</th>
							<th class="px-6 py-4 text-left border-b border-white/10">Valoare (EUR)</th>
							<th class="px-6 py-4 text-left border-b border-white/10">Tip</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2024</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Google Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">2.32</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Real</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2024</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Meta Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">0.94</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Real</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2024</td><td class="px-6 py-4">TikTok Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">0.65</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Real</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2025</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Google Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">2.85</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Est</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2025</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Meta Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">1.15</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Est</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2025</td><td class="px-6 py-4">TikTok Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">0.82</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Est</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2026</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Google Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">3.40</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Pred</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2026</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Meta Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">1.45</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Pred</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="px-6 py-4">2026</td><td class="px-6 py-4">TikTok Ads</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Avg CPC</td><td class="px-6 py-4">1.10</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Pred</td></tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>

			<p>Puteți descărca datele brute în format CSV de aici: <a href="/ppc-benchmarks-2024-2026.csv" class="text-cyan-400">ppc-benchmarks-2024-2026.csv</a></p>

			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">De ce cresc costurile?</h2>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-4">
				<li><strong>Inflație ad-tech:</strong> Costul serverelor și al procesării AI se reflectă în prețurile de licitare.</li>
				<li><strong>Competiție AI:</strong> Mai mulți advertiseri folosesc aceleași unelte de optimizare, ducând la licitări mai agresive.</li>
				<li><strong>Date mai puține:</strong> Pierderea semnalelor third-party crește incertitudinea și, implicit, costul pe acțiune.</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
	</main>
</Layout>
